edu.stanford.nlp.util

Class Trilean

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.util.Trilean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Trilean
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A boolean, but for three-valued logics (true / false / unknown). For most use cases, you can probably use the static values for TRUE, FALSE, and UNKNOWN.
    Author:
    Gabor Angeli
    See Also:
